es.ucm.fdi.gaia.recolibry.api

Class RecommenderResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.ucm.fdi.gaia.recolibry.api.RecommenderResult

  • public class RecommenderResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that contains the result of a recommendation. Its minimum attributes are the recommended object, for example a movie, and a recommended Value, for example a predicted rating.
